            </div>
            <div class="strategy-component">
                <h2>User-Friendly Interface</h2>
                <p>Prioritize user experience and accessibility in app or web design. Conduct user testing and feedback sessions during development.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="strategy-component">
                <h2>Security and Compliance</h2>
                <p>Implement robust security measures for data protection and privacy. Ensure compliance with international travel and health regulations.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="strategy-component">
                <h2>Marketing and Adoption</h2>
                <p>Launch a comprehensive marketing campaign to promote the ecosystem to travelers and businesses. Offer incentives for early adopters.</p>
